{"tid":1950452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★上季家庭負債佔GDP急升至80.4%創新高","createTime":"2020-03-30T10:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T01:50:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"faaafa8a1b30b058a33b656bd72be7f99cabf6f7","tid":1950452,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:39:51.000Z","msg":"香港金管局的數據顯示，由於香港經濟在2019年第3季開始顯著收縮，令家庭負債佔本地生產總值(GDP)的比率，由2019年第2季的75.8%，進一步上升至2019年第4季的80.4%，為歷史新高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGDP可代表整體香港收入，家庭負債佔GDP比率愈低，代表香港家庭負債愈低，償還能力愈高，反之亦然。換言之，目前比例達80.4%，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">意味着香港家庭還債能力下降，只要失業率飆升，形勢將更為惡劣。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200330/bkn-20200330174613040-0330_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200330%2Fbkn-20200330174613040-0330_00842_001.html&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2UcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=f7fa01aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200330/bkn-20200330174613040-0330_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a4dfa9e38748115dc63853bdbd783ec9bc67b3e2","tid":1950452,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb7b50e3a60062d0739a9f57a04e349bc43a91a","tid":1950452,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pcAEs3H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2